    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p>
            I am a Ph.D. candidate with an interdisciplinary focus on sustainable energy systems, integrating data analysis,
            mathematical modeling, and artificial intelligence. My research spans agrivoltaic systems, optimization, and predictive
            modeling, providing innovative solutions to pressing challenges in renewable energy and agriculture.
        </p>
    </section>

